<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank You!</h1>
        <p>Your exam has been submitted. We will notify you of your score soon.</p>
        <p>You can close the tab.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>